---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Contact Goldstone LLC
meta_title: Contact Goldstone LLC
meta_description: "Contact Dennis Blancey directly about Lynn Creek Placers, Adelaide Mine, or a Nevada mining property packet from Goldstone LLC."
extra_css:
  - /assets/css/content.css
---
<article class="content-page">
  <header class="content-hero on-bg">
    <div class="content-hero__inner">
      <p class="eyebrow">Direct inquiry</p>
      <h1>Contact Goldstone LLC</h1>
      <p class="content-hero__lede">Inquiries are reviewed by Dennis Blancey directly. Use the form below to request a property packet or arrange a focused follow-up.</p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="content-section">
    <div class="contact-layout">
      <aside class="contact-card" aria-labelledby="contact-card-title">
        <h2 id="contact-card-title">Contact Card</h2>
        <dl class="contact-card__list">
          <div>
            <dt>Phone</dt>
            <dd><a href="tel:+17754005337">+1 775 400 5337</a></dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt>Phone</dt>
            <dd><a href="tel:+17755448494">+1 775 544 8494</a></dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt>Email</dt>
            <dd><a href="mailto:Grandnevadacorp@gmail.com">Grandnevadacorp@gmail.com</a></dd>
          </div>
          <div>
            <dt>Offices</dt>
            <dd class="mono numerals-data">Carlin NV 89822<br>Golconda NV 89414<br>Carson City NV 89702</dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </aside>

      <section class="inquiry-panel" id="inquiry" aria-labelledby="inquiry-title">
        <p class="eyebrow">Property packet</p>
        <h2 id="inquiry-title">Request Property Packet</h2>
        <form class="inquiry-form" name="inquiry" method="POST" action="/contact/thank-you/" data-netlify="true" netlify-honeypot="bot-field">
          <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="inquiry">
          <p class="form-honeypot" aria-hidden="true">
            <label>Do not fill this out if you are human: <input name="bot-field" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off"></label>
          </p>

          <div class="field">
            <label for="name">Name <span class="required-text">(required)</span></label>
            <input id="name" name="name" type="text" autocomplete="name" required>
          </div>

          <div class="field">
            <label for="company">Company</label>
            <input id="company" name="company" type="text" autocomplete="organization">
          </div>

          <div class="field">
            <label for="email">Email <span class="required-text">(required)</span></label>
            <input id="email" name="email" type="email" autocomplete="email" required>
          </div>

          <div class="field">
            <label for="phone">Phone</label>
            <input id="phone" name="phone" type="tel" autocomplete="tel">
          </div>

          <div class="field field--full">
            <label for="property-interest">Property of interest</label>
            <select id="property-interest" name="property-interest">
              <option value="Lynn Creek Placers">Lynn Creek Placers</option>
              <option value="Adelaide Mine">Adelaide Mine</option>
              <option value="Both properties">Both properties</option>
              <option value="Other / not sure">Other / not sure</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <div class="field field--full">
            <label for="message">Message <span class="required-text">(required)</span></label>
            <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="7" required></textarea>
          </div>

          <button class="btn btn--primary" type="submit">Request property packet</button>
        </form>

        <p class="due-note">Inquiries are reviewed by Dennis Blancey directly. Goldstone LLC does not provide investment advice. Prospective buyers should conduct independent due diligence including title verification, mineral rights review, and on-site inspection.</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </section>
</article>
